headline: RF Q4 Deep Dive: Loan Pipeline Rebound and Technology Modernization in Focus
summary: Regional banking company Regions Financial (NYSE:RF) fell short of the markets revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales falling 2.8% year on year to $1.81 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.57 per share was 6.8% below analystsâ€™ consensus estimates.
